title: Shatter Messiah - Hail The New Cross
description:
Shatter Messiah - Hail The New Cross


Heavy/Power Metal
Releasedate: 2013-10-11

Almost 7 years after their second album 'God Burns Like Flesh' here is finally the next episode. 
U.S. Metal lovers that like music somewhere in between bands like Vicious Rumors, Heathen, Sanctuary, Iced Earth and Nevermore will certainly find a lot they will like on this 'Hail the New Cross' album.


Enjoy // Kay
